.TH HYPRLAUNCHER 1 "2025-11-15" "hyprlauncher 0.1.5" "Hyprland Ecosystem"
.SH NAME
hyprlauncher \- multipurpose launcher and picker for Hyprland
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hyprlauncher
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hyprlauncher
is a multipurpose and versatile launcher and picker for Hyprland, built on
hyprtoolkit.
It provides application launching, file picking, and calculator functionality
powered by libqalculate.
.PP
Multiple data providers are available: Desktop applications, Unicode
characters, Emoji, Math expressions, and Font glyphs.
.B hyprlauncher
runs as a daemon by default for instant access and uses entry frequency
caching to prioritize commonly used items.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-d ", " \-\-daemon
Initialize but do not open the launcher window (daemon mode).
.TP
.BR \-o ", " \-\-options " " \fI"a,b,c"\fR
Pass an explicit comma\-separated option array.
.TP
.BR \-m ", " \-\-dmenu
Read options from standard input in dmenu\-compatible format
(newline\-separated).
.TP
.BR \-t ", " \-\-toggle
Toggle the launcher window instead of opening it.
.TP
.BR \-\-quiet
Disable all logging.
.TP
.BR \-\-verbose
Enable verbose logging.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Print version information.
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Print help message.
.SH CONFIGURATION
The configuration file is searched for at
.IR $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/hypr/hyprlauncher.conf
or
.IR ~/.config/hypr/hyprlauncher.conf .
.SS General options
.TP
.B grab_focus
Grab keyboard focus. Default: 1.
.SS Finders options
.TP
.B default_finder
Default search provider. Default: desktop.
.TP
.B desktop_prefix
Prefix to activate the desktop applications finder. Default: empty.
.TP
.B unicode_prefix
Prefix to activate the Unicode character finder. Default: ".".
.TP
.B math_prefix
Prefix to activate the math expression finder. Default: "=".
.TP
.B font_prefix
Prefix to activate the font glyph finder. Default: "'".
.SH DEPENDENCIES
.BR wl\-clipboard (1)
is required for clipboard integration with the Unicode, Math, and Font
providers.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR Hyprland (1),
.BR hyprland\-run (1)
.SH AUTHOR
The Hyprland Development Team
